description: As fall turns to winter, bright holly berries make their appearance. Winterberry dinnerware by Pfaltzgraff is the holiday classic that brings this timeless motif to life in elegantly sculpted dinnerware and serveware, beautiful glassware, and joyous giftware. Stunningly crafted of dolomite, it's beautifully detailed in festive colors and can be used as a decorative accent on a table or mantel when not filled with cookies. The head serves as a lid and removes for easy access to contents. Measures 11x6.1x7.48 inches. Hand-wash only.
